file.name: required-fields-api-test.yml
file.content:
---
openapi: 3.0.0
info:
  title: Example required fields test API spec
  version: 0.0.1
servers:
  - url: "http://example.com"
paths:
  "/test":
    get:
      tags:
        - test
      operationId: testOperation
      description: test operation description
      responses:
        "200":
          description: Success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: "#/components/schemas/Foo"
components:
  schemas:
    Foo:
      type: object
      required:
        - bar
      properties:
        anything:
          type: boolean
        bar:
          type: string
